251
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:02,250
- I think I'm very creative.

252
00:10:02,250 --> 00:10:04,100
- [Will] What is your biggest weakness?

253
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:06,790
- Sometimes I get a bit stressed.

254
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:09,360
